{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"363fa3bce7","title":"右派言论——诽谤共青团组织","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"357c9f6284","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"363fa3bce7"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"2d2ad5a9a1","name":"陶观兰"},{"id":"2d831ee046","name":"阚开齐"},{"id":"8a7bad3a47","name":"史专贵"},{"id":"8aff656cc4","name":"上海第一师范学院"},{"id":"caa2c58a5c","name":"王德茂"},{"id":"d00c7dd491","name":"任寿春"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f875d58225","type":"title","text":"右派言论——诽谤共青团组织","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"363fa3bce7"},{"id":"818747f656","type":"authors","text":"上海第一师范学院陶观兰王德茂史专贵阚开齐任寿春","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"363fa3bce7"},{"id":"5e5b5d0299","type":"paragraph","text":"“团没有先进性的团员，是乌合之众，党是一个政治没落的集团。”(历史系（一）三班学生陶观兰)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"363fa3bce7"},{"id":"fa0300dda5","type":"paragraph","text":"“团内也因为党导领的结果有宗派主义也只表扬好的共青团，不表扬好的青年群众，团委官僚主义很严重直到昨天还是这样。”(政教科学生王德茂)","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"363fa3bce7"},{"id":"a1606b86b6","type":"paragraph","text":"“支书是户籍警，学生会是派出所，团委就是分局了。”(中文科9班学生史专贵)","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"363fa3bce7"},{"id":"e206df4b81","type":"paragraph","text":"“团委包办一切，学生会有名无实成了傀儡。”(中文科8班)","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"363fa3bce7"},{"id":"26d5ad099d","type":"paragraph","text":"“共青团员和过去的三青团一样。”(中文科22班学生阚开齐 任寿春)","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"363fa3bce7"},{"id":"75785b2fb6","type":"paragraph","text":"团支部是恶势力，反对支部是向恶势力斗争。(历史科6班学生姚育民)","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"363fa3bce7"},{"id":"f16ba9ba9c","type":"paragraph","text":"“团委算什么！张××（指团委宣传部长）是个动摇不定的人他怕我！团委是小头子有事找他有啥用！还是找大头子（指党委）。”(中文科15班学生陈开甲)","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"363fa3bce7"},{"id":"44a26bbc64","type":"paragraph","text":"“县长参加劳动和下乡生活，这都是‘虚伪’”。(语文科（一）5凌其成)","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"363fa3bce7"},{"id":"53500b1226","type":"paragraph","text":"团组织是关门主义，官僚主义是否是‘小人当道，忘成人这美德”。(中文科19班学生李震生)","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"363fa3bce7"},{"id":"1a782c901b","type":"paragraph","text":"“团委只知号召，这批人懂得什么只会空喊口号。”(中文系6班徐庆祯)","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"363fa3bce7"},{"id":"31b61017e0","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《鸣放言论选集》（上海第一师范学院，1957）","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"363fa3bce7"}],"page":{"id":"64067c81dc","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"363fa3bce7","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}